title: Sample Book (USA), ca. 1850
creditline: Gift of Mrs. Louis E. Imershein
description: Twenty-one page swatchbook. Cover in silk with a design of poppies in pink and green on a dark blue ground. Pages of tan, blue, green, red and pink cotton. With 333 samples of crochet and darned net work in linen, cotton and wool thread. Two pink silk ribbons to close.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (USA), ca. 1850; cotton, silk, linen, wool; H x W: 26 x 22 cm (10 1/4 x 8 11/16 in.); Gift of Mrs. Louis E. Imershein; 1967-4-1
